description:
Danny welcomes actress, talk show host, and legend, Rosie O'Donnell! Rosie stars in season 2 of The L Word: Generation Q, which premiered August 8 on Showtime! Danny and Rosie talk about the 25th anniversary of her show, working with Penny Marshall and Nora Ephron, the A League of Their Own reboot, her holiday albums, and SO much more!


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
